"(define-syntax (wrap-*-append stx)
  (syntax-parse
   stx
   [(_ name)
    (with-syntax ([pict:name (datum->syntax
                              stx
                              (string->symbol
                               (string-append "pict:"
                                              (symbol->string
                                               (syntax->datum #'name)))))])
      #'(define (name sep . args)
          ;; prefix
          (pict:name
           ;; sep
           (if (number? sep)
               (list sep)
               (list (default-append-spacing) (maybe-atom->pict sep)))
           ..
           (map maybe-atom->pict args)
           ..)))]))"
